abstract: Georgia wins NCAA women's swimming and diving championship for third time in four years.

headline.print_headline: Georgia Women Win Third Title in Four Years
headline.main: Georgia Women Win Third Title in Four Years

snippet: Georgia won the N.C.A.A. women’s swimming and diving championship for the third time in four years, holding off Stanford and the defending champion California in Atlanta.
lead_paragraph: Georgia won the N.C.A.A. women’s swimming and diving championship for the third time in four years, holding off Stanford and the defending champion California in Atlanta.
